# BloodBridge API

Connecting blood donors with hospitals in real time.

## Setup

```bash
# 1. Install dependencies
pip install -r requirements.txt

# 2. Run the server
uvicorn main:app --reload
```

The server starts at **http://localhost:8000**  
Interactive docs at **http://localhost:8000/docs**

---

## Endpoints

| Method | Path             | Description                          |
|--------|------------------|--------------------------------------|
| GET    | /health          | Health check                         |
| POST   | /register        | Register a new user                  |
| POST   | /login           | Login and receive token              |
| GET    | /donors          | List donors (filter: city, blood_type) |
| POST   | /donors          | Create a donor profile               |
| GET    | /blood-requests  | List blood requests (filter: city, blood_type, status) |
| POST   | /blood-requests  | Submit a new blood request           |
| GET    | /inventory       | List hospital inventory (filter: city, blood_type) |
| POST   | /inventory       | Add/update hospital inventory        |

---

